sequenceDiagram
    actor Applicant
    participant Frontend
    participant Gateway
    participant DocumentService

    Applicant->>Frontend: Open document checklist in application
    Frontend->>Gateway: GET /gateway/documents/{applicationId}/required
    Gateway->>DocumentService: GET /api/document/application/{applicationId}/required
    DocumentService-->>Gateway: 200 OK (required documents checklist)
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 200 OK
    Frontend-->>Applicant: Show required documents list

    Applicant->>Frontend: Select file and upload a document
    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /gateway/documents/upload
    Gateway->>DocumentService: POST /api/document/upload
    DocumentService-->>Gateway: 200 OK (upload success)
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 200 OK
    Frontend->>Gateway: GET /gateway/documents/{applicationId}/required
    Gateway->>DocumentService: GET /api/document/application/{applicationId}/required
    DocumentService-->>Gateway: 200 OK (updated checklist)
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 200 OK
    Frontend-->>Applicant: Update upload status and enable submission when complete
